Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: The building has been used for manufacturing and assembly processes since it was built in the early 1990’s. It has been well maintained and is in excellent condition. From a labor accessibility point of view, it has a prime location being in one of the most densely populated areas of the city and next to the main ring road giving it important flexibility in being able to use either the Zaragoza, Las Americas or Santa Teresa International crossings. Some 85% of the work force of the 4 maquila plants, here in Altavista, walk to work from their homes in the area surrounding the facility.
